title: Got the Facts on Milk x264 AC3 MVGroup.org
description:
Got the Facts on Milk

Science Documentary hosted by Shira Lane, published by Unleashed in 2011 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/f/fa/Got-the-Facts-on-Milk-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Documentary that dared to question the much publicized health benefits of milk and dairy products. A girls quest to find out what is really wrong with the milk, only to be booted off the USDA grounds for asking the wrong questions. Addressing myth, truth and all in-between, the film becomes a humorous yet shocking exposition that provokes serious thought about this everyday staple. Filmed in 2007, directed and produced by Shira Lane. Production Companies - Unleashed Productions and LeTo Entertainment.
